<style>
  #rect {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background-color: green;
    clip-path: shape(nonzero from 256px 10px,
                     hline by 95px, vline by 80%, hline by -1%, close,
                     move to 25px 25px, hline by 51px, vline by 4294967296px, hline by -49%, close);
  }
</style>
<body>
  <p>The test passes if there is a green filled rect.</p>
